org.opendaylight.controller.networkconfig.neutron

Interface INeutronLoadBalancerAware


  • public interface INeutronLoadBalancerAware
    This interface defines the methods a service that wishes to be aware of LoadBalancer Rules needs to implement

    • Method Detail

      • canCreateNeutronLoadBalancer

        int canCreateNeutronLoadBalancer(NeutronLoadBalancer loadBalancer)
        Services provide this interface method to indicate if the specified loadBalancer can be created
        Parameters:
        loadBalancer - instance of proposed new LoadBalancer object
        Returns:
        integer the return value is understood to be a HTTP status code. A return value outside of 200 through 299 results in the create operation being interrupted and the returned status value reflected in the HTTP response.

      • neutronLoadBalancerCreated

        void neutronLoadBalancerCreated(NeutronLoadBalancer loadBalancer)
        Services provide this interface method for taking action after a loadBalancer has been created
        Parameters:
        loadBalancer - instance of new LoadBalancer object

      • canUpdateNeutronLoadBalancer

        int canUpdateNeutronLoadBalancer(NeutronLoadBalancer delta,
                               NeutronLoadBalancer original)
        Services provide this interface method to indicate if the specified loadBalancer can be changed using the specified delta
        Parameters:
        delta - updates to the loadBalancer object using patch semantics
        original - instance of the LoadBalancer object to be updated
        Returns:
        integer the return value is understood to be a HTTP status code. A return value outside of 200 through 299 results in the update operation being interrupted and the returned status value reflected in the HTTP response.

      • neutronLoadBalancerUpdated

        void neutronLoadBalancerUpdated(NeutronLoadBalancer loadBalancer)
        Services provide this interface method for taking action after a loadBalancer has been updated
        Parameters:
        loadBalancer - instance of modified LoadBalancer object
